snippet.title: Death of the Augnob playthrough (home computer,,,,,, PC,,,,, laptop...)
snippet.description:
i still quite enjoy the atmosphere of this 2014 game i made

The augnob face was designed and drawn by bohnz.deviantart.com

Download hereL http://gamejolt.com/games/death-of-the-augnob/26524?comment_page=2

Music:

soundcloud.com/jack-king-spooner (Slime monster song)

metallover95.newgrounds.com (Bar song)

conspiracyamc.bandcamp.com/album/negative-hate-destruction (Desert area ambience, not sure where he got the instrumentals)

durn.newgrounds.com (Club song)

Game by Jake Clover

This game was inspired by some things such as Rocky and the Dodos, The Neverhood, Pingu, Space Funeral, Revenge of the Sunfish and Angus Mckie's sci-fi illustrations.
